  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1079">
<l>uṭuppatūu muṇpatūuṅ kāṇiṟ piṟarmēl </l>
<l>vaṭukkāṇa vaṟṟākuṅ kīḻ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The base will bring an evil (accusation) against others, as soon as he sees them (enjoying) good food and clothing.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
